{
  "stem": "19921.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there was sort of like, like a screen, like a wire screen to enter the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a big-- to this day, I remember, it was a tall, big tank.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to enter, I don't know if it was a small door or not.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was sort of like a wired, a wire gate through the whole, through the whole thing with shoes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had sorted out shoes-- ladies', men's, and children's separately, complete separately.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were thousands of the shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And everybody-- every shoe was sorted out, you know, by pair, it was sorted out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And just there, one shelf after another.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that's what we saw in that thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was ladies' and men's shoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And on the side, again, we saw, you know, a big mountain of ashes, which we did not know what it was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And again, the magazines, you know, with the clothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And finally, we entered a crematorium, which at that time, we did not know a crematorium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the crematorium-- I know there was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was-- the crematorium was made from, from cement, cement blocks, exactly, I don't know the measure, but about 20 feet, about 20 feet by something, I don't remember exactly what.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they had sort of like shower heads on the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We didn't know what-- we thought it was water for shower.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They had very small opening in the steel doors that you can see from the outside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You couldn't see anything from the inside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But you could see from the outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They had small little openings, small windows, sort of with gates on the top of the ceiling, on the side of the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
